                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6379" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1003</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9808 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“追溯重述”还是“未来适用”？——诺泰生物IPO申报前多笔前期差错更正</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">&quot;Retrospective Restatement&quot; or &quot;Prospective Application&quot;? – A Number of Prior Period Error Corrections Before Sinopep Biology IPO Filing</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">许楠，孙伟凡，孙亚淑</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">河北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江苏诺泰澳赛诺生物制药股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药卫生工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">前期差错更正；追溯重述法；未来适用法；重要性；IPO；2022百优案例；微案例;</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Prior period error correction; Retrospective Restatement Method; Prospective Application Method; Significance; IPO</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">前期差错更正是指企业对当期发现的发生在以前会计期间的会计差错进行调整更正，更正方法分为追溯重述法与未来适用法。本案例采用“AB双案例”教学模式，案例A以IPO申报前时任财务总监徐总质疑采用追溯重述法更正多笔前期差错为切入点，具体描述徐总的顾虑以及提议采用未来适用法的思考过程，旨在为学生创设问题情境，引导其自主解决问题；案例B则以审计负责人小陈的视角展开，详细描述小陈打消徐总顾虑且劝服徐总最终决定采用追溯重述法的过程，旨在通过呈现公司的实际决策行为，强化学生对理论知识点的理解并促使其反思此前想法中存在的瑕疵与不足，进而提高自身职业判断能力。本案例围绕追溯重述法与未来适用法的区别展开，引导学生重点掌握前期差错重要性的判断标准以及在企业IPO申报前这一特定环境下的特殊考虑，并分析公司多次进行前期差错更正的原因。在培养学生形成辩证思维和提高职业判断能力的同时，引导学生深刻领悟专业精深、勤勉尽职、知错就改的重要性，真正将思政元素润物细无声地融入课堂教学中。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The prior period error correction refers to the adjustment and correction of the accounting errors found in the previous accounting period by the enterprise. The correction method is divided into Retrospective Restatement method and Prospective Application method. This case uses the &quot;AB double cases&quot; teaching model, Case A before filing in the IPO, then Finance Director Xu questioned the Retrospective Restatement method is used to correct significant prior period error as the breakthrough point, A detailed description of Director Xu concerns and proposed Prospective Applicable method is used to thinking process, aimed at creating problem situation for students, to guide its own solve problems; Case B with the perspective of Audit Director Chen, a detailed description the process of he reassures and persuades Director Xu to adopt Retrospective Restatement method, aims to present the company&#39;s actual decision-making behavior, strengthen students&#39; understanding of theoretical knowledge and promote its reflecting the defects and deficiencies existing in the previous ideas and improve their professional judgment ability. This case focuses on the difference between Retrospective Restatement method and Prospective Application method, and guides students to master the judgment key standards of the importance of prior period errors and the special considerations in the specific environment before the IPO filing of enterprises, and analyze the reasons for the company&#39;s repeated prior period errors correction. At the same time of cultivating students to form dialectical thinking and improve their professional judgment ability, students are guided to deeply understand the importance of professional and sophisticated, diligence and responsibility, and correcting mistakes, so as to truly integrate ideological and political elements into classroom teaching silently.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务会计理论与实务》、《会计学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">前期差错更正方法区别；前期差错更正方法选择依据——重要性的判断；多次前期差错更正的原因；前期差错更正方法账务处理；前期差错更正方法在IPO申报前考虑因素</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-07</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
